{"tha-ap186:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap186:0.2":"Kutajapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap186:0.3":"Pancahatthiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap186:1.1":"“Tisso namasi bhagava, ","tha-ap186:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap186:1.3":"Purakkhato savakehi, ","tha-ap186:1.4":"rathiyam patipajjatha. ","tha-ap186:2.1":"Panca uppalahattha ca, ","tha-ap186:2.2":"catura thapita maya; ","tha-ap186:2.3":"Ahutim datukamoham, ","tha-ap186:2.4":"pagganhim vatasiddhiya. ","tha-ap186:3.1":"Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap186:3.2":"Gacchantam antarapane; ","tha-ap186:3.3":"Buddharamsihi phutthosmi, ","tha-ap186:3.4":"Pujesim dvipaduttamam. ","tha-ap186:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap186:4.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap186:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap186:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap186:5.1":"Ito terasakappamhi, ","tha-ap186:5.2":"panca susabhasammata; ","tha-ap186:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap186:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap186:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap186:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap186:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap186:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pancahatthiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap186:8.1":"Pancahatthiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}